<article id="attorneyOuting">
  <input id="hdnEmployeeID" type="hidden" value="{Model.EmployeeID}" />
  <section id="Announcement" style="margin-right: 20px">
    <table style="width: 100%">
      <tr>
        <td colspan="5">
          <img src="http://localhost:59172/uploads/sunningdalePool.jpg" style="margin-left: 25px; margin-right: 25px" />
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <div class="hr"></div>
    <table border="0" style="width: 100%">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <p>
            Plans are well underway for the Firm Outing which will be held on Tuesday, July 9 at Sunningdale Country Club in Scarsdale, New York.  Please complete the questionnaire below, for yourself and, if applicable, a separate form for your spouse/guest, no later than Monday, June 24. For planning purposes, we are unable to accept submissions after this date.
            <br />
            <br />
            Regardless of whether or not you plan to attend, each employee must complete the top portion of this form.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </section>
